The paper focuses on computer vision techniques for understanding humans in images, which falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The paper covers a wide range of topics, including low-level feature point descriptors, 3D human pose estimation, and high-level fashion-aware models, which suggests that it may also fall under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Additionally, the paper mentions semantic segmentation of clothing and predicting fashionability, which suggests that it may also fall under the categories of multimedia (cs.MM) and graphics (cs.GR).
